        <div class="wwf-phs-border ">
          <h1>Sodexo</h1>
          <p><p><strong><span><span><span><span>Creating healthy and sustainable meals, good for people and planet alike</span></span></span></span></strong></p>

<p><strong><span><span lang="EN-GB"><span>WWF and Sodexo are celebrating working together for 10 years, and 2020 sees us launch a brand new phase of this industry-leading partnership to reduce Sodexo’s carbon footprint.</span></span></span><span>&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
</p>


          

